==同源多倍体类型==
*三倍体：拥有三套染色体，如[[无籽西瓜|无籽西瓜]]以及一些[[缓步动物门|缓步动物门]]的动物<ref>{{cite journal |doi=10.1078/0044-5231-00032 |author=Bertolani R |title=Evolution of the reproductive mechanisms in Tardigrades: a review |journal=Zoologischer Anzeiger |volume=240 |issue=3–4 |pages=247–252 |year=2001 }}</ref>。
*四倍体：拥有四套染色体，如[[陆地棉|陆地棉]]<ref>{{cite journal | author = Wendel J. F. | title = Introduction to polyploid genome evolution and lessons from Gossypium | journal = XVII International Botanical Congress | volume = | issue = | pages = | year = 2005 | month = | pmid = | doi = | url = | isnn = }}</ref>和[[鲑鱼|鲑鱼]]<ref name="StouderBisson1997">{{cite book|author1=Deanna J. Stouder|author2=Peter A. Bisson|author3=Robert J. Naiman|title=Pacific Salmon and Their Ecosystems: Status and Future Options|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=3K9KAocMn0EC&pg=PA30|accessdate=9 July 2013|year=1997|publisher=Springer|isbn=978-0-412-98691-8|pages=30–31}}</ref>。
*六倍体：如普通[[小麦|小麦]]、[[猕猴桃|奇異果]]<ref name=kiwifruit>The genetic origin of kiwifruit. http://www.actahort.org/books/297/297_5.htm {{Wayback|url=http://www.actahort.org/books/297/297_5.htm |date=20210225222314 }}</ref>
*八倍体：如[[中华鲟|中华鲟]]、[[大丽菊|大丽菊]]
*十倍体：某些[[草莓属|草莓]]
*十二倍体：[[青葙|青葙]]、[[大米草|大米草]]<ref>{{cite journal | author = Ainouche M. L., Fortune P. M., Salmon A., Parisod C., Grandbastien M. A., Fukunaga K., Ricou M., Misset M. T. | title = Hybridization, polyploidy and invasion: lessons from Spartina (Poaceae) | journal = Biological Invasions | volume = 11 | issue = 5| pages = 1159–1173 | year = 2009 | month = | pmid = | doi = 10.1007/s10530-008-9383-2 | url =  }}</ref>以及两栖动物[[非洲爪蟾|乌干达爪蛙]]

